name: RESCUES ROCK THE RUNWAY 2011 CALENDAR by TORU®
description:
RESCUES ROCK THE RUNWAY 2011 CALENDAR by TORU® 

Compassion and fashion come together for the very first time in a charity calendar created by TORU called Rescues Rock the Runway.  

A stunning 12 month calendar featuring rescues from Paws 4 You Rescue transformed into super models. This calendar also provides pet lovers with heart warming stories on the lives of shelter dogs and finding their forever homes.  

Proceeds benefit Paws 4 You Rescue, a non-profit dog rescue organization based in Miami, Florida.  

Photography by Andrew Brusso (andrewbrusso.com).  


Also check out Rescue Wear by TORU at torudog.com.
